                <button class="copy-example-btn" id="copy-example-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); copyExampleToPlayground()">

                  <i class="fa-solid fa-copy"></i> 繧ｨ繝・ぅ繧ｿ縺ｸ繧ｳ繝斐・ (螟榊宛蛻ｰ郛冶ｾ大勣)

                </button>

                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down toggle-icon" id="example-toggle-icon" style="transform: rotate(-90deg); transition: transform 0.25s;"></i>

              </div>

            </div>

            <pre id="example-pre-block" style="display: none;"><code class="language-sql" id="lesson-example">SELECT * FROM students;</code></pre>

            <div id="lesson-glossary" style="display: none; padding: 12px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; color: var(--text-muted);">

              <!-- IT Passport key glossary definitions loaded dynamically -->

            </div>

          </div>



