              <span>蜊倩ｪ槭き繝ｼ繝・/ 隸肴ｱ・略蜊｡</span>

              <button class="java-vocab-flip-btn" onclick="javaFlipCard()">鄙ｻ霓ｬ / Flip</button>

              <button class="java-vocab-nav-btn" onclick="javaVocabPrev()"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left"></i></button>

              <button class="java-vocab-nav-btn" onclick="javaVocabNext()"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i></button>

              <span id="java-vocab-counter" class="java-vocab-counter">1 / 1</span>

            </div>

