        <!-- ==================== CODING EXAM WIDGETS ==================== -->

        <!-- Coding Exam Launch Config Screen -->

        <div class="content-card coding-exam-config" id="coding-exam-config" style="display: none;">

          <div class="cbt-config-card">

            <div class="cbt-config-header-main" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">

              <i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code cbt-logo-icon" style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: inline-block;"></i>

              <h2 id="coding-config-title" style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">螳樊桃郛也ｨ区ｨ｡諡溯・ｯ・(螳滓橿讓｡隧ｦ)</h2>

              <p id="coding-config-desc" style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px;">讓｡諡滓律譛ｬ IT 荳馴葎蟄ｦ譬｡逧・ｼ也ｨ玖・ｯ慕識蠅・ょ惠髯仙ｮ壽慮髣ｴ蜀・ｮ梧・扈吝ｮ夂噪郛也∵・謨ｰ謐ｮ蠎謎ｻｻ蜉｡縲・/p>

            </div>



            <div class="cbt-config-options" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin-bottom: 24px;">

              <div class="cbt-option-row" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">

                <label style="font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--neon-cyan);"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i> 閠・ｯ戊ｧ・・ (隧ｦ鬨楢ｦ丞援):</label>

                <ul class="exam-rules-list" style="padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main);">

                  <li>鬚倡岼蝮・ｸｺ<strong>螳樊桃郛也ｨ矩｢・謨ｰ謐ｮ蠎捺衍隸｢鬚・/strong>・檎ｻ呎律譁・枚蟄嶺ｻｻ蜉｡謌夜｢・悄霎灘・扈捺棡縲・/li>

                  <li>謾ｯ謖∝惠蜿ｳ萓ｧ逧・strong>讓｡諡滓ｲ咏將郛冶ｾ大勣</strong>荳ｭ蜊ｳ譌ｶ郛門・縲∬ｿ占｡後∝柱隹・ｯ穂ｻ｣遐√・/li>

                  <li>螳梧・莉｣遐∝錘・檎せ蜃ｻ<strong>窶憺ｪ瑚ｯ∝ｹｶ菫晏ｭ倡ｭ疲｡・(蛻､螳・窶・/strong>霑幄｡梧ｵ玖ｯ慕畑萓区｡鬪後・/li>

                  <li>豬玖ｯ墓・蜉滂ｼ・assed 笨難ｼ芽ｮ｡蜈･蠕怜・・悟庄莉･蜿榊､堺ｿｮ謾ｹ逶ｴ蛻ｰ蛻､螳夐夊ｿ・・/li>

                  <li>隸ｷ蝨ｨ蛟定ｮ｡譌ｶ扈捺據蜑咲せ蜃ｻ<strong>窶懃ｻ捺據閠・ｯ募ｹｶ莠､蜊ｷ窶・/strong>・瑚ｶ・慮邉ｻ扈溷ｰ・・蜉ｨ謾ｶ蜊ｷ縲・/li>

                </ul>

              </div>



              <div class="cbt-option-row" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">

                <label for="coding-exam-count" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;"><i class="fa-solid fa-hashtag"></i> 讓｡諡溯・ｯ暮｢倬㍼:</label>

                <select id="coding-exam-count" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-main); padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; outline: none; font-size: 13px;">

                  <option value="5">5 鬚・(蠢ｫ騾滓ｵ玖ｯ・- 髯先慮 15 蛻・帖)</option>

                  <option value="10" selected>10 鬚・(譬・㊥螳樊桃 - 髯先慮 30 蛻・帖)</option>

                  <option value="15">15 鬚・(蜈ｨ髱｢謖第・ - 髯先慮 45 蛻・帖)</option>

                </select>

              </div>

            </div>



            <button class="cbt-launch-btn" onclick="startCodingExam()" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--neon-blue), var(--neon-cyan)); color: #000; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2); transition: var(--transition-smooth);">

              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-play"></i> 蠑蟋句ｮ樊桃閠・ｯ・(隧ｦ鬨馴幕蟋・

            </button>

          </div>

        </div>



        <!-- Coding Exam Running Session -->

        <div class="content-card coding-exam-panel" id="coding-exam-panel" style="display: none;">

          <!-- Exam Header Info -->

          <div class="exam-header-bar" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">

            <div class="exam-title-box">

              <span class="cbt-indicator-badge" style="background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2); color: var(--neon-cyan); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i> 螳樊桃譛ｺ閠・/span>

              <h4 id="coding-exam-display-title" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 4px;">SQL 螳樊桃閭ｽ蜉帶ｨ｡諡滓ｵ玖ｯ・/h4>

            </div>

            <div class="exam-timer-box" style="background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.25); color: #f87171; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">

              <i class="fa-solid fa-stopwatch"></i> 蜑ｩ菴呎慮髣ｴ: <span id="coding-timer-display">30:00</span>

            </div>

          </div>



          <!-- Active Question Card -->

          <div class="eq-card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">

            <div class="eq-card-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 13px;">

              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">

                <span class="eq-number" id="eq-number-text" style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--neon-cyan);">隨ｬ 1 鬚・/ 蝠・1</span>

                <span class="eq-diff-badge" id="eq-diff-text" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-muted);">髫ｾ蠎ｦ: 笘・・笘・/span>

              </div>

              <button class="eq-flag-btn" id="eq-flag-btn" onclick="toggleCodingQuestionFlag()" style="background: transparent; border: none; color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer; transition: var(--transition-smooth); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">

                <i class="fa-regular fa-flag"></i> 譬・ｮｰ豁､鬚伜､肴衍

              </button>

            </div>



            <!-- Task text details -->

            <div class="eq-body-area" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;">

              <div class="eq-text-ja" style="font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-main);">

                <h5 style="color: var(--neon-cyan); margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i> 繝溘ャ繧ｷ繝ｧ繝ｳ (譌･譁・ｻｻ蜉｡謠剰ｿｰ)</h5>

                <p id="eq-task-ja">蟄ｦ逕溘・繧ｹ繧ｿ縺九ｉ縺吶∋縺ｦ縺ｮ繝・・繧ｿ繧貞叙蠕励＠縺ｪ縺輔＞縲・/p>

