                  <div class="field-score-progressbar" style="height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden;">

                    <div class="field-score-fill" id="coding-results-progress-bar" style="height: 100%; width: 80%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon-blue), var(--neon-cyan)); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--neon-cyan);"></div>

                  </div>

                </div>



                <div class="field-score-item" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-top: 12px; margin-top: 4px;">

                  <span>閠・ｯ慕畑譌ｶ (謇隕∵凾髢・:</span>

